{
  "stem": "21308.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But that was the situation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We knew of it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We didn't now of Dachau and those places, but they were still to come.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I don't even recall Jimmy Rothschild talking about it, although I'm sure he did, but probably not when I was at the meeting.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He didn't come up all that much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So there I was, I was working on a farm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was earning about-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --well, this would be '33.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I was only about a pound a week, just over a pound a week.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But again, you can't relate it on present day costs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that is very difficult to answer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Above all in everybody's mind was the preservation of their own families.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you're a widow, with-- I think my mother's widows' pension was 10 shillings, which, about $0.25, today's money-- and she was expected to keep a family on that for a week.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think their own problems overshadowed everything at that time, in January 1933.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they would be all the heating bills and everything else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Life was very hard in the UK then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Although we are on the victorious side, things were pretty rough going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure we talked about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sure we talked about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think we talked about it I think more from what you might call a pseudo military side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The British Army aided by the French army, such as it was, aided by the Americans, who came in very, very late, had, in fact, destroyed the German command system.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the last thing anybody wanted was another war because there was a War Memorial.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody knew everybody else and there had been this colossal waste of life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Over a million British men and women died in that war.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
